main event: A UFO was sighted over Cambridge City, Indiana on June 30, 1953 around 3:30 AM.
interesting points: The object was described as an 'unknown flying object' (UFOB).
A staff member reported that a UFOB Form 117 was sent to the observer but had not been returned as of July 3, 1953.
There was no physical evidence or photographs taken of the object.
The report indicates that the case was still under investigation as of May 1955.
